 <item> <title>3) Policy and Infrastructure</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/race-top/district-competition/selection-criteria-c-3-policy</link>
 <description>3) Policy and Infrastructure.  Comprehensive policies and infrastructure for learning that provide every student, educator, and level of the education system (e.g., classroom, school, and LEA) with the support and resources they need, when and where they are needed, including: </description>
