 <item> <title>Absolute Priorities</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/race-top/district-competition/absolute-priorities</link>
 <description>For FY 2012 and any subsequent year in which the Department makes awards from any list of unfunded applicants resulting from this competition, the Department will consider only applications that, consistent with 34 CFR 75.105(c)(3), meet Absolute Priority 1 and one of Absolute Priorities 2-5 described below.</description>
