 <item> <title>Eligibility Criteria</title>
 <link>https://www.ed.gov/race-top/district-competition/eligibility-criteria</link>
 <description>
	Eligible applicants include only individual local educational agencies (LEAs) (as defined in this document) and consortia of LEAs.

	LEAs may apply for all or a portion of their schools, for specific grades, or for subject area bands (e.g., lowest-performing schools, secondary schools, feeder pattern, middle school math, or preschool through third grade).
	L</description>
